{"lemma":"خُشُنُ","slug":"خُشُنُ","root":"خ.ش.ن","root_slug":"خ-ش-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ش-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10712","","n10716"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%B4%D9%8F%D9%86%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of خَشِن (ḵašin):; rougher; roughest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of خَشِن (ḵašin):; cruder; crudest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of خَشِن (ḵašin):; coarser; coarsest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of خَشِن (ḵašin):; ruder; rudest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of خَشِن (ḵašin):; tougher (life); toughest (life)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of خَشِن (ḵašin):; hoarser; hoarsest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"rough, harsh, rude"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Elative of خَشِن (ḵašin, “rough, rude”).\n\nColor or defect adjective from the root خ ش ن (ḵ š n); compare خَشِن (ḵašin, “rough, rude”)."},"ipa":["/ʔax.ʃan/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10712","headword_ar":"خَشُنَ","root":"x$n","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$uwnapN","text_ar":"خُشُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$onapN","text_ar":"خُشْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, KL) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$aAnapN","text_ar":"خَشَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(CK, TA, but omitted in some copies of the K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$onN","text_ar":"خَشْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxo$anapN","text_ar":"مَخْشَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, rough, harsh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * KL, PS;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAna","text_ar":"لَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEuma","text_ar":"نَعُمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tx$~n","text_ar":"تخشّن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa *uw xa$onapK","text_ar":"هُوَ ذُو خَشْنَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$uwnapK","text_ar":"خُشُونَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxo$anapK","text_ar":"مَخْشَنَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is difficult, refractory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stubborn; not to be coped with."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$inN","text_ar":"خَشِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$una Ealayohi Sadorihi","text_ar":"خَشُنَ عَلَيْهِ صَدْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh Sdrh","text_ar":"عليه صدره"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ax$w$n","text_ar":"اخشوشن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, angry with him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.) See also 3."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","KL","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n10716","headword_ar":"خَشِنٌ","root":"x$n","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rough, harsh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, * K, KL, PS;) applied to a thing (S, Msb, K) of any kind; (K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$anu","text_ar":"اَخْشَنُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) in relation to a stone, they seldom or never say otherwise than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$anu","text_ar":"اَخْشَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) the fem. of the former is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$unN","text_ar":"خُشُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) [also said to be a pl. by poetic license of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$anu","text_ar":"اَخْشَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$onN","text_ar":"خُشْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as will be seen below,] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xi$aAnN","text_ar":"خِشَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is applied in the sense explained above to land [or lands]: (TA:) the fem. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$anu","text_ar":"اَخْشَنُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$onaA='u","text_ar":"خَشْنَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$onN","text_ar":"خُشْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN xa$inapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ خَشِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged, ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"x$onaA='u","text_ar":"خشْنَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rugged ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which are stones and sand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mulaA='apN","text_ar":"مُلَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$onaA='u","text_ar":"خَشْنَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"[A wrapper for the body] in which is roughness, harshness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarseness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from newness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from make."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)  A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong"},{"kind":"text","text":"man. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa xa$inu AljaAnibi","text_ar":"هُوَ خَشِنُ الجَانِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$anuhu","text_ar":"اَخْشَنُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is difficult, refractory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stubborn; not to be coped with."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA. [See also 1.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaA$a Eayo$FA xa$inFA","text_ar":"عَاشَ عَيْشًا خَشِنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lived a rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarse, life."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$anu","text_ar":"اَخْشَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","JK"]}]}}